com.squareup.wire

Annotation Type ProtoField


  • @Target(value=FIELD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface ProtoField
    Annotates generated Message fields with metadata for serialization and deserialization.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      int tag
      The tag number used to store the field's value.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      boolean deprecated
      True if the field is marked as deprecated.
      Class<? extends Enum> enumType
      For repeated Enum fields, the underlying Enum type.
      Message.Label label
      The field's protocol buffer label, one of Message.Label.OPTIONAL, Message.Label.REQUIRED, Message.Label.REPEATED, or Message.Label.PACKED.
      Class<? extends Message> messageType
      For repeated Message fields, the underlying Message type.
      boolean redacted
      Redacted fields are omitted from toString() to protect sensitive data.
      Message.Datatype type
      The field's protocol buffer datatype, e.g., Datatype#INT32, Datatype#MESSAGE, or Datatype#ENUM.

    • Element Detail

      • tag

        public abstract int tag
        The tag number used to store the field's value.

      • type

        public abstract Message.Datatype type
        The field's protocol buffer datatype, e.g., Datatype#INT32, Datatype#MESSAGE, or Datatype#ENUM. Defaults to Datatype#MESSAGE.
        Default:
        com.squareup.wire.Message.Datatype.MESSAGE

      • label

        public abstract Message.Label label
        The field's protocol buffer label, one of Message.Label.OPTIONAL, Message.Label.REQUIRED, Message.Label.REPEATED, or Message.Label.PACKED. Defaults to Message.Label.OPTIONAL.
        Default:
        com.squareup.wire.Message.Label.OPTIONAL

      • messageType

        public abstract Class<? extends Message> messageType
        For repeated Message fields, the underlying Message type.
        Default:
        com.squareup.wire.Message.class

      • enumType

        public abstract Class<? extends Enum> enumType
        For repeated Enum fields, the underlying Enum type.
        Default:
        java.lang.Enum.class

      • deprecated

        public abstract boolean deprecated
        True if the field is marked as deprecated.
        Default:
        false

      • redacted

        public abstract boolean redacted
        Redacted fields are omitted from toString() to protect sensitive data. Defaults to false.
        Default:
        false
